# Te Pā .vercelignore
# Strategy: exclude heavy, unreferenced asset folders, but include every
# social-kit file that is referenced by index.html / rhizome-mapper.html.
# Audit: see docs/audit-report-* — referenced social-kit files audited
# 2026-06-27 (48 files, ~3.2MB).

# Heavy unreferenced trees served from R2 instead
social-kit/memes/
social-kit/motifs/

# Heavy platform tree — re-include the 5 referenced X-share renders below
social-kit/platform/*
!social-kit/platform/platform-x-koru-begin.png
!social-kit/platform/platform-x-kow-law.png
!social-kit/platform/platform-x-niho-ai.png
!social-kit/platform/platform-x-pa-protect.png
!social-kit/platform/platform-x-tak-future.png

# Distribution bundles — ship via teaching-kits/ + R2, not via static deploy
social-kit/*.zip
social-kit/*.pdf
social-kit/stickers/te-pa-sticker-kit.zip

# Standalone large social-media source PNGs not embedded in the site
assets/social/kiwi-dialectic-banner-x.png
assets/social/kiwi-dialectic-profile-x.png
assets/social/substack-cover.png
assets/social/substack-hero-resistance.png
assets/social/substack-avatar.png
assets/social/kiwi-dialectic-github-symbol.png

# Local-only
index.html.bak
